doctype html
html(lang="en-au")
head
  style(type="text/css").
    body {
      margin: auto;
      display: block;
    }
    body > div > img {
      padding-left: 10%;
    }
    button {
      color: #FFFFFF;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      line-height: 0;
      background-color:#00698F;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 4px;
      width: 160px;
      height: 50px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .content {
      text-align: left;
      padding-left: 10%;
      padding-right: 10%;
      line-height: 24px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .content > img {
      display: block;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .content > a > button {
      display: block;
      margin: auto;
    }
body
  img.image(src="cid:govAUCrest" alt="Australian Government coat of arms")
  <br/>
  p.content
    img.image(src="cid:dataGovLogo" alt="Data gov logo")
    |Hi there, <br/><br/>
    |A query has been raised in relation to a #{agencyName} data set: #{dataset}. 
    |Please log in to your profile on data.gov.au
    |using #{agencyEmail} as soon as possible to respond to this query.<br/><br/>
    |The query is from #{requesterName}, #{requesterEmail}: <br/><br/>
    |#{requesterMsg} <br/><br/>
    a(target="_top" href=`mailto:${requesterEmail}`)
      button(type="button") Reply 
    <br/><br/>
    |The Australian Government has mandated that agencies have a responsibility to be transparent to any public consumer of open data 
    a(href=`https://search.data.gov.au/mandate`). 
    |If you have questions about why you got this email or what to do, email
    |data@digital.gov.au <br/><br/>
    |Sincerely, <br/> <br/>
    |The Digital Transformation Agency at Data.gov.au
